Steps For Static Pod

1. minikube ssh

2. go to etc folder

3. cd kubernetes 

4. cd manifest

5. create a file here (sudo touch file.yml)


6. Wrtie a pod file here


7. sudo systemctl restart kubelet 


8. now ,
           kubectl get pods
           
9. Now you can see your static pod running


10. Even if you delete your pod from here and run the get pod command you still find your static pod running


 
             
